<p style="margin-left:10px;font-size:20px; padding-top:10px;">
    <b style="color:#000;">About the location:</b> In the mid 19th century, Ramakrishna Paramhans set out to revitalize Vedic philosophy and principles amongst the people of India. Following his steps, the Ramakrishna Ashrama, Rajkot, located on a serene campus offers a value based education, has a public library and an Ayurvedic center, plus guest house and a permanent exhibition showcasing the life of Shri Ramakrishna Paramhans.
